                <supplied reason="lost">In</supplied> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Iun</abbr><ex>oni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>eginae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> d<expan><ex>eabus</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>omnib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Ge<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>loc</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Pompeian<lb break="no" n="5"/>us <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>VIII <expan><abbr>Ant</abbr><ex>oninianae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> pro se et <lb n="8"/>suis <expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>mnibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Idibus <expan><abbr>Ian</abbr><ex>uariis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">G</supplied>rato et Seleu<lb break="no" n="2"/>co co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Aus mehreren Fragmenten zusammengesetzt. Auf der rechten Nebenseite ein Blitzbündel. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona, Z. 11/12 auf der crepido. Zahlreiche Ligaturen. (B): Schillinger-Häfele; AE 1978; Cubaynes: Z. 6: [l]eg(ionis); Schleiermacher: Z. 9: p(onendum) [c(uravit)]; Schillinger-Häfele; AE 1978; Schleiermacher: Z. 10: Ia[n(uariis); Schleiermacher; Schillinger-Häfele; AE 1978: Z. 11: [Gr]ato.</p>
            </div>
